headline: Hilton Worldwide Holdings: Valuation Still Makes Sense, But Technicals Suggest Some Caution
summary: Hilton Worldwide Holdings remains resilient, leveraging its asset-light, fee-based model and strong brand to deliver revenue growth and margin stability.
